data.description: **CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS** This beautiful 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath brick home is located on the outskirts of Malone. It sits on a spacious 5-acre lot setback from the road with a beautiful canopy drive providing plenty of space to roam and enjoy the beauty of nature. This property boasts an array of fruit trees such as satsumas, lemons, olives, blueberries, blackberries, figs, scuppernong and many others. It also offers a large barn with 3 stalls perfect for horses. There is also housing for chickens, quail, rabbits and a separate fenced pasture for goats. (Some fencing needs repair) This house is warm and inviting with a cozy wood burning fireplace. The kitchen comes equipped with gas or electric hookup for your stove and beautiful tile flooring. Its secluded charm offers you peace and tranquility. It's a perfect retreat for nature and animal lovers alike.  This house has everything you are looking for.  Call today to see if this is a place you could call home!
